fields.name: AmlWorkspaceId
fields.description: The ID of a Azure Machine Learning workspace to link with Databricks workspace

fields.name: CustomPrivateSubnetName
fields.description: The name of the Private Subnet within the Virtual Network

fields.name: CustomPublicSubnetName
fields.description: The name of a Public Subnet within the Virtual Network

fields.name: CustomVirtualNetworkId
fields.description: The ID of a Virtual Network where this Databricks Cluster should be created

fields.name: EnableNoPublicIP
fields.description: Should the Public IP be Disabled?

fields.name: Encryption
fields.description: Contains the encryption details for Customer-Managed Key (CMK) enabled workspace.

fields.name: LoadBalancerBackendPoolName
fields.description: Name of the outbound Load Balancer Backend Pool for Secure Cluster Connectivity (No Public IP).

fields.name: LoadBalancerId
fields.description: Resource URI of Outbound Load balancer for Secure Cluster Connectivity (No Public IP) workspace.

fields.name: NatGatewayName
fields.description: Name of the NAT gateway for Secure Cluster Connectivity (No Public IP) workspace subnets.

fields.name: PrepareEncryption
fields.description: Prepare the workspace for encryption. Enables the Managed Identity for managed storage account.

fields.name: PublicIPName
fields.description: Name of the Public IP for No Public IP workspace with managed vNet.

fields.name: RequireInfrastructureEncryption
fields.description: A boolean indicating whether or not the DBFS root file system will be enabled with secondary layer of encryption with platform managed keys for data at rest.

fields.name: ResourceTags
fields.description: Tags applied to resources under Managed resource group. These can be updated by updating tags at workspace level.

fields.name: StorageAccountSkuName
fields.description: Storage account SKU name, ex: Standard_GRS, Standard_LRS. Refer https://aka.ms/storageskus for valid inputs.

fields.name: VnetAddressPrefix
fields.description: Address prefix for Managed virtual network. Default value for this input is 10.139.
